SELECT
E.EVENT_ID, E.USER_ID,
E.EVENT_TYPE, E.EVENT_TIMESTAMP,
U.COUNTRY, U.PLAN_TYPE
FROM RAW_EVENTS E
INNER JOIN USERS U
ON E.USER_ID = U.USER_ID
WHERE E.EVENT_TYPE = 'purchase'
LIMIT 20;
